# smoke-classification-baseline.txt

The sibling baseline file is for pre-existing unclassified smoke helper names.
It is grandfathering data for BACKLOG #61, not the place to classify new work.

New pins go to manifest, not baseline: add `<helper_name> <class>` to
`tests/smoke-proves-manifest.txt` using `docs/smoke-pin-classification.md`.

Deliberate baseline edits are review-visible convention debt, not
machine-rejected. Treat a baseline diff as something reviewers should notice and
ask about.
